race.comment: INSANE (3) hit the ground running and on speed early but faded out of it to finish fifth (26.04) at this track over 460m. Form from his last run is proving strong. Should be very hard to beat this time. KIANI STAR (4) produced a modest effort most recently when sixth at Ballarat over 390m behind Fortune Hunter (22.67) in a Grade 5 H. Worth following up. BALLAN BRUMBY (7) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Anchor Cranker (22.78) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Form from his last run is proving strong. Expecting another good run. WALK WITH PRIDE (8) will give backers a sight.
